{"pin":"BH00112","subcodes":[{"code":"BH00112","anchor":"","title":"Suriy-i-Asma' (=Lawh-i-Ibn?)","first_line":"The fragrance of sorrows hath encompassed the Beauty of the All-Merciful, and the gates of joy and delight have been shut fast through the tyranny of the people of rebellion [3.5s]... ...Know thou that when the Son of Man yielded up His breath to God, the whole creation wept with a great weeping.","first_line_orig":"رایحه احزان جمال رحمن را احاطه نموده و ابواب فرح و بهجت از ظلم اهل طغیان من  ","language":"5","word_count":"3990","subjects":"@rejection by the people of the Bayan, @the Word of God; influence and centrality of, @exhortations and counsels, @teaching the Cause; call to teach, @expressions of grief; lamentation; sadness","notes":" \u003ca href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20070930181707/http://bahai-library.com/resources/leiden.list/leiden.list.html#294\"\u003eLL#294\u003c/a\u003e,  \u003ca href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20070930181707/http://bahai-library.com/resources/leiden.list/leiden.list.html#380\"\u003eLL#380\u003c/a\u003e","translations":[],"writing_refs":[{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"sv","lang_name":"Swedish"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"te","lang_name":"Telugu"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"fa","lang_name":"Persian"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"fr","lang_name":"French"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"hu","lang_name":"Hungarian"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"ko","lang_name":"Korean"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"pl","lang_name":"Polish"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"tvl","lang_name":"Tuvalu"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"vi","lang_name":"Vietnamese"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"zh-Hant","lang_name":"Traditional Chinese"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","lan